original: Asum, Kristianst. 1., av Per A. o. Ida Nrls’s0’n. G. 34 m. Karin Holmquist, f. Täc;km’an. — Stud:ex. i Krrstian-st. 24, veterrkand. 28, veter:ex. 31. Ve-teriförordn. på iskilda platser 31-39, di-’striktsveterinär i Ullared fr. 39.
translated: Asum, Kristianstad 1st district, son of Per A. and Ida Nrls's0'n. Married in 1934 to Karin Holmquist, born Täckman. He graduated from high school in Kristianstad in 1924. He became a veterinary assistant in 1928, and a veterinarian in 1931. He was a veterinary substitute in various places from 1931-1939, and a district veterinarian in Ullared from 1939 onwards.
